				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I have a level 18 monk on the E'ci server and just recently I got the blackened wand in Befallen. Befallen is located in West Commons on the South side of the zone(the desert).  The npc that drops this item is located on the third level inside the secret room, in the very left alcove.  He is a dark elf named Priest Amiaze.  As for the sapphire, that's in Najena, which is north of Nektulos Forest, in Lavastorm.  The guy you're looking for is named Erekos(something like that) and as stated before, he spawns near Rathyl. Just look on the map and you'll be able to find where Rathyl spawns.<BR>
